branchCategory.name: C(D)QS, Compact Cylinder, Double Acting, Single Rod, Anti-lateral Load
branchCategory.description: <p>The CQS anti-lateral load, single rod, double acting version of the compact cylinder is available for those small bore cylinder applications where saving space is a concern. This increased side load version (CQS*S) is available for more demanding applications. The CQS offers standard up to 50mm. Both switch capable and non-switch capable body styles are the same, and switches can be mounted on three (12-16 bore) and four (20-25 bore) sides.</p>
